    <p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0393c03"/><lb ed="T" n="0393c03"/><persName key="A002294">釋僧<ptr target="fn21"/>慧</persName>，姓劉，不知何許人。在<placeName key="PL000000027771">荊州</placeName>數十<lb ed="T" n="0393c04"/>年。<placeName key="PL000000025203">南陽</placeName><persName key="A002973">劉虬</persName>立<placeName key="PL000000027840">陟屺年</placeName>，請以居之。時人見<lb ed="T" n="0393c05"/><persName key="A002294">之</persName>已五六十年，終亦不老。舉止<ptr target="fn22"/>趨爾，無甚<lb ed="T" n="0393c06"/>威儀。往至病人家，若瞋者必死，喜者必差，<lb ed="T" n="0393c07"/>時咸以此為讖。凡未相識者，並悉其親<lb ed="T" n="0393c08"/>表存亡。<ptr target="fn＊"/><persName key="A002294">慧</persName>嘗至<placeName key="PL000000000150">江</placeName>邊，告津吏求度。吏迫<lb ed="T" n="0393c09"/>以舟小，未及過之。須臾已見<ptr target="fn＊"/><persName key="A002294">慧</persName>在彼，兩<lb ed="T" n="0393c10"/>岸諸人咸歎神異。<placeName key="PL000000002516">中山</placeName><persName key="A002648">甄恬</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000027798">南平</placeName><persName key="A003285">車曇</persName>同日<lb ed="T" n="0393c11"/>請<ptr target="fn＊"/><persName key="A002294">慧</persName>。<ptr target="fn＊"/><persName key="A002294">慧</persName>皆赴之。後兩家檢覆，方知分身。</p><p><lb ed="T" n="0393c12"/><date key="j18974971901513" notAfter-iso="0494" notBefore-iso="0483">齊永明中</date>，<persName key="A002654">文<ptr target="fn＊"/>慧</persName>要下<placeName key="PL000000008975">京</placeName>，行<ptr target="fn＊"/>過<persName key="A002296">保誌</persName>。<persName key="A002296">誌</persName>撫背<lb ed="T" n="0393c13"/>曰：「<persName key="A002294">赤龍子</persName>。」他無所言。<ptr target="fn＊"/><persName key="A002294">慧</persName>後還<placeName key="PL000000027771">荊</placeName>，遇見鎮<lb ed="T" n="0393c14"/>西長史<persName key="A003286">劉景[(麩-夫+玉)-來+(卄/(素-糸))]</persName><!-- Unicode=26f06 -->，忽泣慟而<ptr target="fn23"/>投之。數日，<persName key="A003286">[(麩-夫+玉)-來+(卄/(素-糸))]</persName>果<lb ed="T" n="0393c15"/>為刺史所害。後至<placeName key="PL000000028642">湘州城</placeName>南，忽云地中有<lb ed="T" n="0393c16"/>碑。眾人<ptr target="fn24"/>試掘，果得二枚。<ptr target="fn＊"/><persName key="A002294">慧</persName>後不知所終。<lb ed="T" n="0393c17"/>或云<date key="j19033451904141" notAfter-iso="0501" notBefore-iso="0499">永元中</date>卒於<placeName key="PL000000027766">江陵</placeName>。</p><p>時<placeName key="PL000000027743">江陵長沙寺</placeName>又有<lb ed="T" n="0393c18"/><persName key="A003287">釋慧遠</persName>者，本沙門<persName key="A003288">慧印</persName>之<ptr target="fn25"/>蒼頭<!-- 奴僕 -->也。<persName key="A003288">印</persName>見其<lb ed="T" n="0393c19"/>有信，因為出家。仍行般舟之業。數歲勤苦，<lb ed="T" n="0393c20"/>遂有神異，能分身赴請，及預記興亡等。</p>
